She looked at HotRod and ran after him in lioness mode."Hey, your not

DarkMouse::
She looked at Drillbit.  He looked bored and anxious at the same time.
"Relax new one.  Megatron works as Megatron sees fit.  He shall see 
you in his own good time."  She lightly touched her bruised cheek.
"Just be careful not to make him mad."
